data.description: Motivated sellers! *ASSUMABLE LOAN OPTIONS AVAILABLE* This home is practically turn-key ready and waiting for you to take a step inside! 4-bedroom house, nestled in the coveted Lago Mar community. From the entryway, a sense of warmth and refinement envelops you. This meticulously maintained residence exudes elegance and tranquility, a pristine escape from the hustle and bustle of daily life. Unique upgrades include an in-home speaker system as well as a custom designed fireplace at the heart of the home. Effortless cleaning becomes a reality with the convenient whole in-house vacuum system, elevating maintenance to new heights. Beyond the captivating features of the house, the Lago Mar community offers a wealth of additional amenities including a 2-acre crystal clear lagoon, sand filled beaches/boardwalk to provide plenty of space for outdoor dining and activities.
